Class Bulbasaur

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--Bulbasaur
All Implemented Interfaces:
Pokemon
public class Bulbasaur
extends java.lang.Object
implements Pokemon

A Bulbasaur is a Pokemon that maintains information about its level, speed, strength, special, defense, total health, current health, experience points, name, attack names, and it's pokemon number. A Bulbasaur knows how to return its level, speed, total health, current health, experience points taken, experience points given, name, attack names, attack strength, pokemon number, image, and damage taken. A Bulbasaur can set its experience points and its current health. A Bulbasaur can also level up and heal itself.
